column16: Steve Pearce called out on strikes.

Ryan Flaherty grounds out, first baseman Brian McCann to pitcher Chaz Roe.
Caleb Joseph flies out to center fielder Brett Gardner.
David Ross walks.   Xander Bogaerts to 2nd.
Xander Bogaerts singles on a line drive to left fielder Martin Prado.   Daniel Nava scores.

Mike Napoli out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Carlos Beltran.   Yoenis Cespedes scores.
